data.description: Welcome back to this stunning property! Step inside to newly installed wood flooring, discover a spiral staircase and balcony with scenic views. The lower level features primary bedroom, an office, and secondary full bathroom. Open floor plan connects the living room, lounge area, two dining spaces. Marvel at the floor-to-ceiling stone wall surrounding the fireplace. The kitchen boasts an oversized island, double oven, butler's pantry, and exquisite craftsmanship with crown molding and curved walkways.Upstairs, three more bedrooms, a full bathroom, and flexible living area. The turf backyard invites relaxation with a covered patio. Energy-efficient with SOLAR PANELS, ensuring a low to no electricity bill. APPRAISED at $415k there’s equity. Previous buyers financing fell through, making this home available once again. Newly installed dishwasher. List price or above,refrigerator, washer, and dryer are included. Additional $5000 incentives available with preferred lender. MOTIVATED SELLER
